                        <h1 class="flex gap-3  text-h5 text-sebase font-bold font-primary pb-2"> Why is DEI important for funders? <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
